						"title": "Get a free API risk assessment",
						"subtitle": null,
						"copy": "APIs have helped evolve the Internet into the place we know it as today. If you have a mobile app, SaaS platform integration, or GenAI implementation, you rely on APIs. But as with any technology changes, this recent explosion of APIs—accounting for 58% of all dynamic traffic, according to Cloudflare's network data—also increases the size of our attack surfaces. \n\nThat's why we created Cloudflare's API Risk Assessment: a complimentary offer intended to help your organization discover its API attack surface. At the end of the assessment, you will receive an executive-level summary report with our recommended remediations for you to leverage internally within your organization.\n\n__Why sign up for an API Risk Assessment?__\n- __Know your attack surface__: Discover API endpoints and identify previously unknown risks—including shadow APIs, BOLA attacks, and data leakage risks. \n- __Discover shadow AI__: AI security starts with discovery. Identify shadow Generative AI endpoints in your public-facing websites to begin securing your AI real estate.\n- __Protect your end-users' data and meet compliance__: Identify when sensitive data is unintentionally exposed via APIs, and meet a growing number of regulatory requirements that require an inventory of all public-facing assets.\n\n[Sample API Risk Assessment — Executive Summary Report](https://cfl.re/api-risk-assesment)",
